      <title>渣打银行在交易大丰收后利润超过预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/standard-chartered-profit-tops-estimates-on-wealth-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行(Standard Chartered Plc)公布的第一季度盈利超出预期，原因是其交易员从动荡的信贷和大宗商品市场中获得了意外之财。]]></description>
